{"tid":1248831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好走呀 要捱到聽日接更","createTime":"2019-06-21T14:30:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T14:50:26.000Z","uid":231206,"like":24,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7cf9f954087c6add339a470f9eb0bfe4b575a1d5","tid":1248831,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:30:45.000Z","msg":"大家唔好走呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">黎緊係星期六日 只要現場一日仲有人<br />\n有數之不盡嘅人都會出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n萬事起頭難 現場一直有人嘅話 想出黎嘅就唔會擔心無人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家出黎嘅意欲就會高好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n相反如果一走 聽日就<span style=\"color: red;\">好難由零開始圍過</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以請大家堅持到日頭 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">等新血黎左補位先返去休息</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後返去抖左既 星期日再出黎補聽日留守班兄弟既位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nE.G. 宜家係現場既: <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">今日留-&gt;聽日返去抖-&gt;後日出返黎</span></span><br />\n返左去既: <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">休息-&gt;聽日盡早黎補位-&gt;後日等兄弟黎補位先走</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申: 非鍵盤戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4256ecbbe6e985d32af501c17ff513067a88e999","tid":1248831,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:31:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e14158734ddc7399ec48d816e3f80e3e848ac23d","tid":1248831,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:32:59.000Z","msg":"大家唔好剩係正評唔推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係屋企既都請幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比更多人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8c51d37e9b20d9ae322073ff1b1ef15c12f383f","tid":1248831,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:33:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28b3dd48da72c95b11b4353f399d5f5668278aea","tid":1248831,"uid":231206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:34:58.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"845b434ab9e16dd1de9b6ce8fd3b91c5342351ad","tid":1248831,"uid":195493,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:35:23.000Z","msg":"班狗最鍾意凌晨過晒尾班車就清場<br />\n現場要睇情況識散呀<br />\nbe water my friend"},{"pid":"aefea36811632bd2f39bd0de85c6382ab8c43991","tid":1248831,"uid":30408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:35:23.000Z","msg":"走定唔走？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1248789\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1248789</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2d091f23193b587430da79f168442942b2d54d56","tid":1248831,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:35:28.000Z","msg":"回家吧"},{"pid":"dcc8060efc4f8b20371e2c43b5e9e8dbf9431c40","tid":1248831,"uid":228244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T14:36:03.000Z","msg":"唔好衝，我哋仲要攞和平獎用作籌碼鬥落去！"},{"pid